content.rendered:
This is more than a gig. Belgian band Amenra, for the first time, will perform live in Cyprus.

Amenra live show it is an experience that gets under your skin. Born in the grey heart of Kortrijk, they have been crafting their own sound landscapes for years, blending post-metal, sludge, and hardcore, full of emotion, spirituality, and power. With hypnotic rhythms soaked in raw emotion, Amenra evokes an unparalleled atmosphere. Universal pain, spiritual hunger, and raw, poetic vocals that shift from screams to whispers. The band has an unparalleled ability to connect art and emotion and their immersive video projections and rituals also add an extra dimension to their intense live shows. You will walk away from the show and you will need to compose yourself, to recenter, to return to society from that place of inner reflection. Nothing will ever be the same after this show.
